{%- comment -%}
  Aurora — third-party integrations loaded in <head>.

  KLAVIYO (email capture + abandoned cart)
  ----------------------------------------
  1. Create a free Klaviyo account, then go to Settings → API keys and copy
     your PUBLIC API KEY (a short 6-character "Company ID", e.g. ABC123).
  2. Paste it between the quotes below and save. Leave empty to disable.

  This single script powers everything: the on-site signup popup, any
  embedded forms, on-site tracking, and the abandoned-cart / abandoned-browse
  flows (those flows are switched on inside Klaviyo, not here).
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign klaviyo_company_id = '' -%}
{%- if klaviyo_company_id != blank -%}
  <script async type="text/javascript" src="https://static.klaviyo.com/onsite/js/klaviyo.js?company_id={{ klaviyo_company_id }}"></script>
{%- endif -%}
